<br>
Zildrax would also be &quot;neutral&quot;, he is a fully selfless individual, cares only about serving his people, Empire, and god best he can, hates deciet, lieing or treachery of any sort, and will gladly sacrifice himself for an Iksar he's never even met before. He is completely loyal to his Empire, above all else. Alot of Iksar are like that, and I can't call that &quot;evil&quot;.<br>
<br>
Also there is the fact that Iksar would not favor grouping or associating with &quot;evils&quot; more then anyone else. Infact they'd most likely detest it, seeing as they have completely opposed ideals to Iksar most of the time.<br>
<br>
